            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ESo%20often%20when%20we%20walk%20through%20a%20crushing%20experience%2C%20we%20feel%20like%20God%20is%20a%20million%20miles%20away.%20The%20enemy%20tells%20us%20that%20God%20does%20not%20care%20and%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20our%20problems.%20David%20reminds%20us%2C%20however%2C%20that%20God%20is%20nearest%20to%20us%20when%20we%20are%20broken%20in%20heart.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20the%20earth%20was%20dark%20and%20without%20form%2C%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%20was%20hovering%20over%20the%20waters%20(Genesis%201%3A2).%20Never%20forget%3A%20Whenever%20your%20life%20seems%20dark%20and%20no%20solution%20is%20in%20sight%2C%20the%20Spirit%20of%20God%20is%20actually%20hovering%20over%20you%2C%20guarding%20you%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20trial.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESomeone%20once%20said%2C%20%22When%20you%20have%20a%20broken%20heart%2C%20you%20must%20give%20God%20the%20broken%20part.%22%20David%20gave%20God%20his%20broken%20heart%20in%20repentance%20after%20his%20sin%20with%20Bathsheba%20and%20reminded%20God%20that%20%22the%20sacrifice%20you%20want%20is%20a%20broken%20spirit.%20A%20broken%20and%20repentant%20heart%2C%20O%20God%2C%20you%20will%20not%20despise%22%20(Psalm%2051%3A17).%20God%20responded%20by%20healing%20David's%20broken%20heart%20and%20restoring%20his%20soul.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYou%20must%20bring%20your%20broken%20heart%20to%20God%20and%20let%20Him%20heal%20it%2C%20for%20a%20%22broken%20spirit%20saps%20a%20person's%20strength%22%20(Proverbs%2017%3A22).%20Go%20to%20Jesus%20with%20your%20broken%20heart%2C%20for%20He%20was%20anointed%20to%20%22comfort%20the%20brokenhearted%22%20(Isaiah%2061%3A1).%20Why%20not%20reach%20out%20and%20ask%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20to%20touch%20you%20where%20no%20human%20surgeon%20can%3F%20He%20is%20near.%20Let%20Him%20do%20His%20work%20right%20now.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
