            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Nehemiah.11:1-12:26",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ENehemiah%2011%3A1-12%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_1%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ENehemiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20People%20Occupy%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20the%20people%20were%20living%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20the%20holy%20city.%20A%20tenth%20of%20the%20people%20from%20the%20other%20towns%20of%20Judah%20and%20Benjamin%20were%20chosen%20by%20sacred%20lots%20to%20live%20there%2C%20too%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20stayed%20where%20they%20were.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_2%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20people%20commended%20everyone%20who%20volunteered%20to%20resettle%20in%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_3%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EHere%20is%20a%20list%20of%20the%20names%20of%20the%20provincial%20officials%20who%20came%20to%20live%20in%20Jerusalem.%20(Most%20of%20the%20people%2C%20priests%2C%20Levites%2C%20Temple%20servants%2C%20and%20descendants%20of%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20servants%20continued%20to%20live%20in%20their%20own%20homes%20in%20the%20various%20towns%20of%20Judah%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_4%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20some%20of%20the%20people%20from%20Judah%20and%20Benjamin%20resettled%20in%20Jerusalem.)%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging-sp%22%3EFrom%20the%20tribe%20of%20Judah%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl%22%3EAthaiah%20son%20of%20Uzziah%2C%20son%20of%20Zechariah%2C%20son%20of%20Amariah%2C%20son%20of%20Shephatiah%2C%20son%20of%20Mahalalel%2C%20of%20the%20family%20of%20Perez.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_5%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAlso%20Maaseiah%20son%20of%20Baruch%2C%20son%20of%20Col-hozeh%2C%20son%20of%20Hazaiah%2C%20son%20of%20Adaiah%2C%20son%20of%20Joiarib%2C%20son%20of%20Zechariah%2C%20of%20the%20family%20of%20Shelah.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eson%20of%20the%20Shilonite.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_6%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20were%20468%26%23xA0%3Bdescendants%20of%20Perez%20who%20lived%20in%20Jerusalem%26%23x2014%3Ball%20outstanding%20men.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_7%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20tribe%20of%20Benjamin%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl%22%3ESallu%20son%20of%20Meshullam%2C%20son%20of%20Joed%2C%20son%20of%20Pedaiah%2C%20son%20of%20Kolaiah%2C%20son%20of%20Maaseiah%2C%20son%20of%20Ithiel%2C%20son%20of%20Jeshaiah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_8%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20him%20were%20Gabbai%20and%20Sallai%20and%20a%20total%20of%20928%26%23xA0%3Brelatives.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_9%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ETheir%20chief%20officer%20was%20Joel%20son%20of%20Zicri%2C%20who%20was%20assisted%20by%20Judah%20son%20of%20Hassenuah%2C%20second-in-command%20over%20the%20city.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_10%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20priests%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl%22%3EJedaiah%20son%20of%20Joiarib%3B%20Jakin%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_11%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20Seraiah%20son%20of%20Hilkiah%2C%20son%20of%20Meshullam%2C%20son%20of%20Zadok%2C%20son%20of%20Meraioth%2C%20son%20of%20Ahitub%2C%20the%20supervisor%20of%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_12%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EAlso%20822%26%23xA0%3Bof%20their%20associates%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20Temple.%20Also%20Adaiah%20son%20of%20Jeroham%2C%20son%20of%20Pelaliah%2C%20son%20of%20Amzi%2C%20son%20of%20Zechariah%2C%20son%20of%20Pashhur%2C%20son%20of%20Malkijah%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_13%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3Ealong%20with%20242%26%23xA0%3Bof%20his%20associates%2C%20who%20were%20heads%20of%20their%20families.%20Also%20Amashsai%20son%20of%20Azarel%2C%20son%20of%20Ahzai%2C%20son%20of%20Meshillemoth%2C%20son%20of%20Immer%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_14%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20128%26%23xA0%3Bof%20his%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E11%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Etheir.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20outstanding%20associates.%20Their%20chief%20officer%20was%20Zabdiel%20son%20of%20Haggedolim.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_15%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20Levites%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl%22%3EShemaiah%20son%20of%20Hasshub%2C%20son%20of%20Azrikam%2C%20son%20of%20Hashabiah%2C%20son%20of%20Bunni.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_16%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EAlso%20Shabbethai%20and%20Jozabad%2C%20who%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20work%20outside%20the%20Temple%20of%20God.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_17%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EAlso%20Mattaniah%20son%20of%20Mica%2C%20son%20of%20Zabdi%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Asaph%2C%20who%20led%20in%20thanksgiving%20and%20prayer.%20Also%20Bakbukiah%2C%20who%20was%20Mattaniah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20assistant%2C%20and%20Abda%20son%20of%20Shammua%2C%20son%20of%20Galal%2C%20son%20of%20Jeduthun.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_18%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20all%2C%20there%20were%20284%26%23xA0%3BLevites%20in%20the%20holy%20city.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_19%22%20bk%3D%22nehe%22%20ch%3D%2211%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20gatekeepers%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl%22%3EAkkub%2C%20Talmon%2C%20and%20172%26%23xA0%3Bof%20their%20associates%2C%20who%20guarded%20the%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22nehe_11_20%22%20bk%3D%22